#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can configure your Bluetooth devices for the &plasma; "
"Workspace."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani lahko konfigurirate svoje naprave Bluetooth za &plasma; "
"Workspace."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please press the <guibutton>Enable</guibutton> button to enable the "
"&bluetooth; subsystem in your operating system."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Omogoči</guibutton>, da omogočite &bluetooth; "
"podsistema v vašem operacijskem sistemu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&bluetooth; &systemsettings; module</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&bluetooth; &systemsettings; module</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&bluetooth; &systemsettings; module</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&bluetooth; &systemsettings; modul</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Configure...</guibutton> button to change the general "
"&bluetooth; settings for your &plasma; Workspace."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Konfiguriraj ...</guibutton>, da spremenite "
"splošno &bluetooth; nastavitve za &plasma; Delovni prostor."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configuring the general module settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija splošnih nastavitev modula</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configuring the general module settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija splošnih nastavitev modula</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make your &bluetooth; device <guilabel>Enabled</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Visible</guilabel> for other &bluetooth; devices with the "
"corresponding items."
msgstr ""
"Svoj &bluetooth; naprava <guilabel>omogočena</guilabel> in <guilabel>vidna</"
"guilabel> za druge &bluetooth; naprave z ustreznimi predmeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to change the &bluetooth; subsystem behavior on receiving "
"file. Your &plasma; Workspace can <guilabel>Ask for confirmation</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Accept for trusted devices</guilabel> (see the <guilabel>Trusted</"
"guilabel> in the device settings below) and <guilabel>Always accept</"
"guilabel> the sent files. You can also configure the folder to store the "
"received files."
msgstr ""
"Možno je spremeniti &bluetooth; obnašanje podsistema pri prejemu datoteke. "
"Vaša &plasma; Workspace lahko <guilabel>Vpraša za potrditev</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Sprejme za zaupanja vredne naprave</guilabel> (glejte "
"<guilabel>Zaupanja vreden</guilabel> v spodnjih nastavitvah naprave) in "
"<guilabel>Vedno sprejme</guilabel > poslane datoteke. Prav tako lahko "
"konfigurirate mapo za shranjevanje prejetih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96 index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please press the back button at the top of the page to return to the main "
"page of the configuration module."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb za nazaj na vrhu strani, da se vrnete na glavno stran "
"konfiguracijskega modula."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a &bluetooth; device to the main list by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button. Your neighborhood will be scanned for "
"available devices. If the device you want to use is not shown in the "
"scanning list then you will need to consult its manual for the instructions "
"on how to set it up."
msgstr ""
"Dodate lahko &bluetooth; napravo na glavni seznam s klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton>. Vaša soseska bo pregledana za razpoložljive "
"naprave. Če naprava, ki jo želite uporabiti, ni prikazana na seznamu "
"skeniranja, boste morali za navodila, kako jo nastaviti, prebrati njen "
"priročnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the <guilabel>Manual PIN</guilabel> if needed and "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton>-click on the detected device to pair it with "
"your computer. See the device manual on the procedure of pairing, the "
"mileadge may vary but usually, it is very straightforward."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi konfigurirajte <guilabel>Ročni PIN</guilabel> in "
"<mousebutton>leva</mousebutton>kliknite zaznano napravo, da jo seznanite z "
"računalnikom. Oglejte si priročnik naprave za postopek združevanja, "
"kilometrina se lahko razlikuje, vendar je običajno zelo preprosta."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding &bluetooth; device</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodajanje &bluetooth; naprava</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding &bluetooth; device</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodajanje &bluetooth; naprava</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton>-click on the list item to configure its name "
"in the devices list and make it <guilabel>Trusted</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Blocked</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Leva</mousebutton>-kliknite na element seznama, da "
"konfigurirate njegovo ime na seznamu naprav in ga naredite "
"<guilabel>Zaupanja vreden</guilabel> in <guilabel>Blokiran</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Device settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve naprave</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Device settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve naprave</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When hovering with the mouse cursor, every &bluetooth; device in the main "
"list shows two buttons on the right."
msgstr ""
"Ko lebdite s kazalko miške, vsaka &bluetooth; naprava na glavnem seznamu "
"prikazuje dva gumba na desni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146 index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"network-"
"connect.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"or <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"network-"
"disconnect.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> to connect or disconnect a device."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"network-connect.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> ali <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"network-disconnect.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon> za povezavo ali odklop naprave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can remove a device from the main list by selecting it and then clicking "
"on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon."
msgstr ""
"Napravo lahko odstranite z glavnega seznama tako, da jo izberete in nato "
"kliknete ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-"
"remove.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to switch &bluetooth; off for some reason press the "
"<guibutton>Disable &bluetooth;</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če morate preklopiti &bluetooth; iz neznanega razloga pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Onemogoči &bluetooth;</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Tray Operation"
msgstr "Delovanje sistemske vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must be running the &plasma; desktop or another suitable window manager "
"in order to display &bluetooth; in the system tray."
msgstr ""
"Morate izvajati program &plasma; namizje ali drug primeren upravitelj oken "
"za prikaz &bluetooth; v sistemski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &bluetooth; module by default displays an icon in the system tray. The "
"icon provides both control and monitoring status indications. A normal "
"&bluetooth; icon indicates that all devices are disconnected, while the icon "
"with the horizontal dotted line indicates that some devices are connected to "
"your computer."
msgstr ""
"&bluetooth; modul privzeto prikaže ikono v sistemski vrstici. Ikona "
"prikazuje tako stanje nadzora kot spremljanja. Običajni &bluetooth; ikona "
"označuje, da so vse naprave prekinjene, medtem ko ikona z vodoravno črtkano "
"črto označuje, da so nekatere naprave povezane z vašim računalnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hover the mouse cursor over the system tray icon, a summary of the "
"connected device list is displayed as a tooltip."
msgstr ""
"Če kazalec miške premaknete nad ikono v sistemski vrstici, se kot opis "
"orodja prikaže povzetek seznama povezanih naprav."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton>-click on the system tray icon to toggle "
"between displaying and hiding the <link linkend=\"controlpanel\">&bluetooth; "
"main control panel</link>."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Leva</mousebutton>-kliknite na ikono v sistemski vrstici za "
"preklop med prikazom in skrivanjem <link linkend=\"controlpanel"
"\">&bluetooth; glavna nadzorna plošča</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton>-click on the system tray icon to display "
"its context menu with just one item:"
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desna</mousebutton>-kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici, da "
"prikažete kontekstni meni s samo enim elementom:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &bluetooth;"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj &bluetooth;"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts the <link linkend=\"kcmbluetooth\">&plasma; &bluetooth; configuration "
"module</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zažene <link linkend=\"kcmbluetooth\">&plasma; &bluetooth; konfiguracijski "
"modul</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &bluetooth; main control panel"
msgstr "&bluetooth; glavna nadzorna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &bluetooth; main control panel can be used to control your computer's "
"&bluetooth; subsystem."
msgstr ""
"&bluetooth; glavno nadzorno ploščo lahko uporabite za nadzor vašega "
"računalnika &bluetooth; podsistem."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&bluetooth; tray control panel</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&bluetooth; nadzorna plošča pladnja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&bluetooth; tray control panel</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&bluetooth; nadzorna plošča pladnja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top row of the panel contains the &bluetooth; switcher to enable or "
"disable the &bluetooth; module, the <quote>plus</quote> button to <link "
"linkend=\"adddevice\">add &bluetooth; devices</link>, and the "
"<quote>configure</quote> button to start the <link linkend=\"kcmbluetooth"
"\">&plasma; &bluetooth; configuration module</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zgornja vrstica plošče vsebuje &bluetooth; stikalo za omogočanje ali "
"onemogočanje &bluetooth; modul, gumb <quote>plus</quote> za <link linkend="
"\"adddevice\">dodajanje &bluetooth; naprave</link> in gumb "
"<quote>konfiguriraj</quote> za zagon <link linkend=\"kcmbluetooth\">&plasma; "
"&bluetooth; konfiguracijski modul</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main space of the panel is devoted to the paired devices."
msgstr "Glavni prostor plošče je namenjen seznanjenim napravam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <guilabel>v</guilabel> button at the right of the device item "
"to expand its properties."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guilabel>v</guilabel> na desni strani naprave, da razširite "
"njene lastnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Send file...</guibutton> button will be shown only if the "
"corresponding device is connected and ready to receive files. This feature "
"may need some additional software to be installed. If needed, please follow "
"the instructions and consult your distribution documentation."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Pošlji datoteko ...</guibutton> bo prikazan le, če je "
"ustrezna naprava povezana in pripravljena za sprejem datotek. Ta funkcija bo "
"morda zahtevala namestitev dodatne programske opreme. Po potrebi sledite "
"navodilom in si oglejte distribucijsko dokumentacijo."
